, shortness of breath, or syncope.', 'Metabolism, Synergism', 'Caution is advised if tacrolimus is used concomitantly with azole antifungal agents.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/168184/', '', 'Cefixime, Secnidazole, Anidulafungin, Micafungin, Oteseconazole, Salicylic acid, Thiabendazole, Ciclopirox, Econazole, Tioconazole, Chlorphenesin', 'Minoxidil, Deoxycholic acid, Calcium gluconate, Magnesium sulfate, Glycopyrronium, Pimecrolimus, Aminobenzoic acid, Ivermectin, Caffeine, Dupilumab, Tralokinumab, More', 1767369485);
